  "_comment_architecture": [
    "PPWR ownership transfer: filled beverage bottles ship from the",
    "bottling plant (manufacturer) to a brand owner's distribution",
    "centre. Standard owning-party source/destination plus a Purchase",
    "Order / Despatch Advice pair so the chain of custody is auditable.",
    "Inline product attributes (euppwr:packagingTier, recyclabilityGrade,",
    "harmonisedSymbol, deposit-return scheme) live inside",
    "masterDataAvailableFor on the product entry, same discipline as",
    "the commissioning template.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,",
    "                              euppwr=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/ppwr/",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
